dsDescriptionValue.value: Spatial data collected during archaeological seasons 2011, 2012 and 2014. Data contain surveyed points, Kite Aerial Imagery, 3D models and close range photogrammetry imagery.

files.description:
Terrace 10, FoxHill locality, Sabaloka, Sudan.
Images obtained by Kite Aerial Photography. The ZIP archive containe derived Digital Terrain Models and orthophotos derived from Kite imagery. The Agisoft Photoscan was used for 3D model creation. Further is included computation report, Ground Control Points (shape file) and surveyed points used for DTM quality evaluation. Further information are in the metadata.txt. 
Due to the large ammount of data and complicated spatial data structure is the file compressed and password protected (to avoid self-unpacking within the dataverse environment). Password: sudan.

files.description:
SFAP (Small Format Aerial Photography) taken from an UAV by GoPro hero 3+ and Sony NEX7 - derived Digital Surface Model was used to estimate the quality of the 3D model produced from the GoPro images (Agisoft PhotoScan used). The testing area is in Eastern Slovakia - the Ondava river meanders.
Due to the large ammount of data and complicated spatial data structure is the file compressed and password protected (to avoid self-unpacking within the dataverse environment). Password: sudan.
